    you're hurting over there too. I guess maybe I'm just selfish, maybe I want to share with you so <br>
    you can feel the hurt I'm feeling. Maybe I just suck. But wow. I am crushed. <br><br>

    You are my everything. This letter, this photo gallery, it was all my way of coping with <br>
    the fact that we're no longer together. To be honest, I really really thought I was the boy <br>
    for you. I really did. And to see it all gone truly crushes me. But love comes with trust, and <br>
    I trust that you made the right decision. Even if it hurts me now, to the point where I can't even <br>
    begin to process this breakup to its entirety, I can stick to the fact that I treated you in the best <br> way that I could have, and at the end of the day, I have loved every second of this time with you. <br> <br>

    I love you Jenna. I love you, I love you, I love you. I honestly don't know what's going to happen. <br> 
    I'm at a loss- I'm completely confused and just... Everything is shut down. My brain is on autopilot <br>
    mode. I can't think straight. I know you know me as someone who can think clearheaded even when it's <br>
    hard, but with you lovie, with you I can't, I just can't handle this hurdle right now. It'll take time, <br>but all I can cling on to are the memories that we had. <br>
    All the times I rubbed your nose, brushed your hair out of your face, all the times you fit under my <br>
    in that little nook, I think back to those and cry, cry, cry. Cry tears of happiness, tears of saddness<br>
    It's all so bittersweet. I am so thankful to you for giving me this time with you, but at the <br>
    same time I'm so fucking sad that it's over. <br>  <br>

    I hope you find what you are looking for. I really do. I don't know what else to write <br>
    to be honest, I haven't thought through it all yet just because it's too painful and I don't <br>
    think my mind is ready for it. But I do know that I still love you and want all the best for you. <br><br><br>

    Take care, my lovebug.<br>
    Yours, <br><br>
    Alex
    
